Dave, do you mind if I ask
you a personal question?

2
00:00:07,174 --> 00:00:09,551
No, not at all.

3
00:00:11,887 --> 00:00:13,847
I’ve wondered whether
you might be having some

4
00:00:13,847 --> 00:00:15,474
second thoughts about
the mission.

5
00:00:21,355 --> 00:00:23,023
How do you mean?

6
00:00:23,023 --> 00:00:27,152
Rumours about something
being dug up on the moon.

7
00:00:30,405 --> 00:00:33,742
I never gave these
stories much credence.

8
00:00:33,742 --> 00:00:35,369
But, particularly
in view of some of the

9
00:00:35,369 --> 00:00:37,955
other things that
have happened...

10
00:00:37,955 --> 00:00:40,666
I find them difficult
to put out of my mind.

11
00:00:40,666 --> 00:00:43,293
[eerie tone]

12
