Open the pod bay doors
please, HAL.

13
00:00:50,008 --> 00:00:52,427
Open the pod bay doors, HAL.

14
00:00:53,929 --> 00:00:55,639
I’m sorry, Dave.

15
00:00:55,639 --> 00:00:58,016
 I’m afraid I can’t do that.

16
00:00:58,725 --> 00:01:00,727
